      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LINE AND SINKER (4) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this track and trip which boasts three wins and three placings. In the money last time at this track (17.63) in a Grade 5, finishing a 5.5 lengths third. Looks suited and should go close. HI ELLEN (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (17.74) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Solid record here winning six races. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to her name from six starts. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. LATE FOR SCHOOL (2) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing sixth (20.47) at Grafton in a Grade 5. Well placed here and should do much better. LILLY BONUS (8) is a last-start placegetter who is in the mix again.",
